Marla Schaffel https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marla_Schaffel 0 Marla Schaffel (born April 17, 1968) is an American actress, especially in musical theatre, noted for her award winning performance in the title role in the musical adaptation of Jane Eyre.
